{"tid":982822,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"嘉熙400伙貨尾下月推 嘉華：有機會減價","createTime":"2019-01-15T12:10:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-16T00:52:36.000Z","uid":174649,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"df684695c252af4aa9201ddfe167cbc08081a11e","tid":982822,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T12:10:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190115/large/1547540962_0dee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190115%2Flarge%2F1547540962_0dee.jpg&h=9a5f06c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大埔區多個新盤低價推出。嘉華國際（173）國際營業及市場策劃總經理（香港地產）溫偉明表示，旗下大埔嘉熙的貨尾單位約400伙最快農歷新年後重推，間隔主要為3房及一堆特色單位。對於定價方面，他表示，<strong><ins>「價錢有機會向下調整」</ins></strong>，不過要因應推盤市況而定。目前項目累售710多伙，套現60多億元。"},{"pid":"c05766c7f09635af39315b04d8efb31f377d462c","tid":982822,"uid":78791,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T12:13:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4bd4b6e1b7e853ce48f3dabd36c605653cbdf349","tid":982822,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T13:24:53.000Z","msg":"講明減價咁搞笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbce82baed1db55a1e83d3161e58017463cca46d","tid":982822,"uid":76745,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T13:30:33.000Z","msg":"400伙大部分係3房同特色單位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n座底600呎 14k一呎就至少8.5m 13k一呎就至少8m <br />\n平過8球 之前買左兩房果啲應該會癲<br />\n貴過9球 使撚買佢"},{"pid":"34392cb9d4a483704a088cdb33fb4b6a66e9643d","tid":982822,"uid":13739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T13:37:28.000Z","msg":"發展商強調有減價空間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63b5a9635228612e0b7671874c51ca282439263a","tid":982822,"uid":76745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"34392cb9d4a483704a088cdb33fb4b6a66e9643d","tid":982822,"uid":13739,"like":0,"dislike